    <searchtitle>Class: PATIENT - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
 with a specific disease or condition who receives treatment from a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>
 or any 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_registrable_birth">REGISTRABLE BIRTH</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
It is an entry on the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 master index.        </p>
      <p>
This will be a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>, which includes 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_neonate">Neonates</xref>, who use a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_bed">Hospital Bed</xref>
 in order to receive clinical care/treatment or someone attending an 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_out-patient_clinic">Out-Patient Clinic</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_day_care_facility">Day Care Facility</xref>, etc.        </p>
      <p>
It will also include people in the community receiving care under a specific 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nhs_service_agreement">NHS SERVICE AGREEMENT</xref>
Â forming part of 'nursing care in the community'. This also includes 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 on the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_elective_admission_list">ELECTIVE ADMISSION LIST</xref>
 who are awaiting 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_elective_admission">Elective Admission</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
